ProjectTitle: The induced dynamics from a nonequilibrium and active environment
InitialFeedbackHistory:
27/06/2022
Good DMP but the layout makes it hard to read, easiest to use DMPonline (https://dmponline.kuleuven.be/) for your future DMPs.  
You don't have to describe your publication strategy in a DMP, here you can focus on the data underlying your publications. 
You can now also use KU Leuven RDR or KU Leuven gitlab to preserve and share data and to make them available for reuse: https://www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/rdr; https://gitlab.kuleuven.be/
